title: Skip Garden Kitchen
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Organic, Western, Mediterranean, Take-out
description: The teaching organic garden and kitchen at the King's Cross regeneration site offers seasonal food created by the youngsters involved in the garden. From 10am scones, tea, and coffee. From 12 lunch. Then cakes, teas and coffees til 4pm. Accepts booking for private events.
streetAddress: off Tapper Walk, behind Lewis Cubbit Square
